  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508920/extras/3b0849d834063da907157ddd23e21964.avif?t=1644077855\" width=600 height=330 /></span><br><br>A sweet love that began in a coffee shop.<br>One is lively and lively, the other is mysterious and gentle.<br>How do you choose?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508920/extras/d339ccf4fb318bc48d0c2394f182f94b.avif?t=1644077855\" width=600 height=292 /></span><br>Role introduction：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508920/extras/e636b7c74930f6de29ce935dbcaff07c.avif?t=1644077855\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>An apprentice Barista.He doesn't work very hard and often plays smart.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508920/extras/2aabaf9a7e2d33d35c5a26b96bcfc290.avif?t=1644077855\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Trainee pastry chef.With a gentle character and a sense of mystery.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508920/extras/30cda63cf00ce320a1eb85d922198c1b.avif?t=1644077855\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>A lively guy. She hesitated between the postgraduate entrance examination and blind date marriage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508920/extras/f7048d23076113d39a2b3d778b3fdfaa.avif?t=1644077855\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Next door youth. The relationship with the hero is very good.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508920/extras/2e